CatDescriptText: The banner on the third floor of the building reads, "You. . .Owe It To Yourself, Democrats and Republicans, Vote For William P. Young, for City Council Nov. 3rd".  The storefront window list the hours of Dr. Jas. H. Cole Surgeon Dentist Dr. U.S. Wharton, MD, physician who share the second floor of building and a broadside in the pharmacy's storefront window has a number of broadsides one reads, "Dance at the union Hall, Fri.,  Nov. 13, 1953".
TitMainTitle: Exterior view of offices and campaign headquarters for William P. Young for City Council, above Med Centre Pharmacy and Ulysses L. Wharton, MD
